Quiz 26 Slider

1. Which options should you change to limit the value of the slider between 1 and 10?

- E and F

2. What do the Transition options apply to?

- Just the handle

3. Which GameObjects make up a slider?

- A background image, fill image and handle image

4. How does the slider change the size of the Fill GameObject?

- By keeping a reference to its Rect Transform

5. How would you change the colour of the slider fil?

- Change the colour on the slider fill child object

6. How can I change the default position of the slider to be centered?

- Make the Value = 30